/     %p There's definitely a place for point ratings in the wine industry; but points aren't really what Bloocher is about. Fundamentally Bloocher is about the wisdom of crowds: Are you getting quince in that gewurztraminer? Look at its cloud and see if other bloochers got quince too. If you decide you like gewurztraminers that show quince, click around some, and maybe we can find a few more. You can opt in to follow your favorite wineries, winemakers, and vineyards, and create your own list of wines and wineries that your friends can use to follow you. We don't like getting spammed any more than you do, so our #{link_to "privacy policy", privacy_path} treats your privacy the way we wish all websites would ours.   

